 thesis also broadly surveys the object search\nliterature, proposing taxonomies in object search problem settings, methods and\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2023 16:41:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 May 2023 04:02:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-05"}
