ology can be used and verified\nto identify the bioaccessibility of lycopene before using it as a functional\nfood ingredient for therapeutic treatments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2023 03:33:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Feb 2023 01:46:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 13 May 2023 05:51:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 18 May 2023 05:05:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-19"}
